115
00:07:03,153 --> 00:07:04,253
Astaga.

116
00:07:04,253 --> 00:07:07,753
Hei, Noboru, jangan bicara terlalu keras.

117
00:07:07,753 --> 00:07:09,153
Yuuta.

118
00:07:09,153 --> 00:07:12,053
